<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/anna-mcmorrin> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Anna McMorrin was appointed Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State in the Wales Office on 7 September 2025. She was previously Assistant Whip, House of Commons between 10 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. She was elected as the MP for Cardiff North in June 2017."@en .
